<Narrow title="Capitalize string">
    <Title>Capitalize string</Title>
    <Subheadline class="block mt-2">02/03/2020</Subheadline>

    <Prose class="mt-6">
        <Paragraph>
            A small helper function to capitalise the first word in a string.
        </Paragraph>

        <CodeBlock>export const capitalize = string => {
return string.charAt(0).toUpperCase() + string.substring(1)
}</CodeBlock>
    </Prose>
</Narrow>